                <ul>
                    <li>TS: Web Applications Development with Microsoft .NET Framework 4</li>
                    <li>Programming in HTML5 with JavaScript and CSS3</li>
                    <li>Programming in C#</li>
                    <li>Developing ASP.NET MVC 4 Web Applications</li>
                </ul>

            </p>

